<br>
Some idiot jackass like &quot;mtdover&quot; whose best arguments are &quot;wah I have a right to my opinion&quot;, &quot;wah the redneck ignorant jackasses who live near me would beat you up&quot;, and &quot;even though I know nothing about you, I'm sure I could beat you up because I'm so tough and you're a pansy&quot;...  these are the sorts of people you can never hope to discuss things with because they're just too damned stupid.  There are other people who, while they may not agree with your point of view, may listen to your arguments and weigh them against their own beliefs.<br>
